    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I left, I think, maybe around two weeks, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and the inquisition started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I found out-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] next, you know, like I  told you, the army offered me to be in the army to make a career in the army.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they promised me to go to study more, which continued to study after the war to complete to be the same officers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One star, you have to continue to go another six months to spend it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I decided I don't want to be a military person.",
